          :markdown
            The `site` jQuery plugin allows you to open or close
            the mobile menu part programmatically.
            
            ```js
            // Toggle the mobile menu part using a toggle boolean
            $('.site').site('toggleMenu', shouldOpen)
            
            // Show the mobile menu part
            $('.site').site('showMenu')
            
            // Hide it
            $('.site').site('hideMenu')
            ```

